# Public Content Audit Allowlist
#
# Literal patterns (one per line). Lines matching any pattern are exempt
# from ALL block and warn checks. Lines starting with # are comments.
# Case-insensitive matching.

# --- Glasswing proper names (Anthropic's program) ---
Project Glasswing
Glasswing-Anthropic
Glasswing-class
Glasswing/Mythos

# --- NVIDIA technology ---
Optimus PRIME
PRIME render-offload

